				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${n}_{c,s}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M72"><mml:msub><mml:mrow><mml:mi>n</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mrow><mml:mi>c</mml:mi><mml:mo>,</mml:mo><mml:mi>s</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="41467_2021_26779_Article_IEq34.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> cells of a specific cell type <inline-formula id="IEq35"><alternatives><tex-math id="M73">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
