				\begin{document}$$Z(x)$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M176"><mml:mi>Z</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:mo>(</mml:mo><mml:mrow><mml:mi>x</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mo>)</mml:mo></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="41467_2021_26779_Article_IEq82.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> and two left-censored gamma distributions <inline-formula id="IEq83"><alternatives><tex-math id="M177">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
