      <p id="Par103">Additionally to the DE analyses, the use of scRNA-seq for the detection of expression quantitative trait loci (eQTLs) was evaluated. We distinguish for the eQTL power between genes with high and with low expression levels, where the mean is used to parameterize a simulation. Therefore, the eQTL power is a function of the mean expression level.</p>
