      <p id="Par105">The implementation pwr.f2.test of the R package pwr is used for the F-test<sup><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR20">20</xref></sup>. The degrees of freedom of the numerator are 1 and of the denominator are <inline-formula id="IEq108"><alternatives><tex-math id="M237">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
