      <p id="Par112">The power of the simulation was compared with the analytic power calculated by scPower to assess at which value of the mean <inline-formula id="IEq132"><alternatives><tex-math id="M289">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
