				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\frac{i}{G}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M296"><mml:mfrac><mml:mrow><mml:mi>i</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mrow><mml:mi>G</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:mfrac></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="41467_2021_26779_Article_IEq135.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> of the gamma mixture model parameterized by the mean UMI counts to obtain the mean <inline-formula id="IEq136"><alternatives><tex-math id="M297">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
