      <p id="Par120">The FDR is the fraction of false positives among all rejected null hypotheses (predicted positives), which includes both the false positives and the true positives. Based on the probability integral transform, the distribution of <italic>p</italic> values for the <inline-formula id="IEq144"><alternatives><tex-math id="M313">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
